arts.ttl: Beth Mead takes bragging rights over partner Vivianne Miedema after pre-match warning
arts.sum: Vivianne Miedema joked her and partner Beth Mead would "not be friends" as England took on the Netherlands at the Women's Euros, but the Lioness had the last laugh

arts.ttl: Vivianne Miedema and partner Beth Mead ‘will not be friends’ during Women’s Euro 2025 clash
arts.sum: The Netherlands captain and Lionesses forward have banned themselves from discussing Wednesday’s clash in Zurich
